data.description: Charming single story pool home on a corner lot in the Dutch Village, French Valley. FULLY PAID FOR SOLAR SYSTEM! Nicely landscaped backyard with inground pool and spa. Built in BBQ. 3 car garage. Sellers are offering a buyer credit of up to $10,000 for interior painting and flooring of the buyer's choice, to be done after close of escrow. House presently shows normal wear and tear. All kitchen appliances have been replaced within the last 2 months to one year. The pool has a new pump motor replaced September 2023.  This is an opportunity for buyers to make the interior of the home the way they want it, with their choice of wall colors and flooring. Top rated Temecula School District. Close to Winchester Rd for easy freeway access to I. 15 and I. 215. Low property tax area currently at less than 1.1%. 27 panel, 7 Kw solar system is fully paid for.
